  <para style="h">2 Basessaloniika</para>
  <para style="toc1">Ebbaluwa ya Pawulo Eyookubiri eri Basessaloniika</para>
  <para style="toc2">2 Basessaloniika</para>
  <para style="toc3">2Bs</para>
  <para style="mt2">Ebbaluwa ya Pawulo Eyookubiri eri</para>
  <para style="mt1">Basessaloniika</para>
  <para style="imt">Ennyanjula</para>
  <para style="ip">Pawulo Omutukuvu yawandiika ebbaluwa eno nga wakati w’emyaka <char style="sc">ad</char> 50 ne 54 nga kyajje amale okuwandiikira Abasessaloniika ebbaluwa eyasooka. Omulamwa gw’ebbaluwa eno ge madda ga Mukama waffe Yesu Kristo. Abantu abamu baali bayigirizza Abasessaloniika mu ngeri ey’obulimba nga babagamba nti olunaku olw’okusalirako emisango lutuuse, era nti oboolyawo eyo y’ensonga evaako okuyigganyizibwa okunene bwe kutyo. Pawulo abawandiikira ng’akakasa abakkiriza nti ddala Kristo agenda kukomawo awooyewooye era asanyuse abakkiriza, naye abo abababonyaabonya agenda kubabonereza (<char style="xt"><ref loc="2TH 1:7">1:7</ref>, <ref loc="2TH 1:8">8</ref></char>). Era nabategeeza nti olunaku olw’okusalirako emisango, lwe lunaku lwa Mukama, terugenda kubatuukako nga tebamanyi, naye Abakristaayo bagenda kulaba ebintu bingi ebigenda okubeerawo nga biddiriragana (<char style="xt"><ref loc="2TH 2:3">2:3</ref></char>). Olw’okubanga kikakafu ddala nga Kristo agenda kukomawo, embeera y’Abakristaayo mu bulamu bwabwe tesaana kubeerako kamogo.</para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 16:1">Bik 16:1</ref>; <ref loc="1TH 1:1">1Bs 1:1</ref></char>
    </note>Nze Pawulo ne Sirwano<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1:1 </char><char style="fq" closed="false">Sirwano </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Mu Luyonaani oluusi ayitibwa Siira</char></note> ne Timoseewo tuwandiikira Ekkanisa ey’Abasessaloniika, abantu ba Katonda Kitaffe ne Mukama waffe Yesu Kristo, <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 1:7">Bar 1:7</ref></char></note>ekisa n’emirembe ebiva eri Katonda Kitaffe ne Mukama waffe Yesu Kristo, bibeerenga nammwe.</para>
  <para style="s1">Okwebaza n’Okusaba</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TH 3:12">1Bs 3:12</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Kitugwanidde okwebazanga Katonda bulijjo ku lwammwe abooluganda, nga bwe kisaana, kubanga okukkiriza kwammwe kweyongedde nnyo okukula, awamu n’okwagalana kwammwe mwekka na mwekka, <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:4 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 7:14">2Ko 7:14</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TH 1:3">1Bs 1:3</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TH 2:14">1Bs 2:14</ref></char></note>ekyo ne kituleetera ffe ffennyini okubeenyumiririzaamu mu kkanisa za Katonda olw’okugumiikiriza kwammwe n’okukkiriza kwammwe wakati mu kuyigganyizibwa kwammwe kwonna awamu n’okubonaabona bye mugumiikiriza. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PHP 1:28">Baf 1:28</ref></char></note>Ako kabonero akalaga nti Katonda mutuukirivu mu kulamula kwe, mmwe mulyoke musaanire obwakabaka bwa Katonda, bwe mubonaabonera, <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 3:25">Bak 3:25</ref>; <ref loc="REV 6:10">Kub 6:10</ref></char></note>ate ng’abo ababanyigiriza alibabonereza nga bwe kibagwanidde. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TH 4:16">1Bs 4:16</ref>; <ref loc="JUD 1:14">Yud 14</ref></char></note>Era nammwe abanyigirizibwa muliweerwa wamu naffe ekiwummulo, mu kubikkulirwa kwa Mukama waffe Yesu bw’aliva mu ggulu, ne bamalayika be ab’amaanyi, <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:8 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GAL 4:8">Bag 4:8</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 2:8">Bar 2:8</ref></char></note>mu muliro ogwaka, n’abonereza abo abatamanyi Katonda era abajeemera Enjiri ya Mukama waffe Yesu. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:9 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PHP 3:19">Baf 3:19</ref>; <ref loc="2PE 3:7">2Pe 3:7</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TH 2:8">2Bs 2:8</ref></char></note>Abo baliweebwa ekibonerezo kya kuzikirira emirembe n’emirembe, nga baawukanyiziddwa ne Mukama waffe, n’ekitiibwa ky’amaanyi ge. <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:10 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 3:13">1Ko 3:13</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 17:10">Yk 17:10</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 1:6">1Ko 1:6</ref></char></note>Bw’alijja okugulumizibwa mu batukuvu be ku lunaku luli abo bonna abamukkiriza balyewuunya kubanga mwakkiriza bye twabategeeza ku ye.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:11 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">nny 5 </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TH 1:3">1Bs 1:3</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Kyetuva tubasabira bulijjo, Katonda waffe abasaanyize okuyitibwa kwammwe. Abawe amaanyi mutuukirize ebirungi byonna bye mukola, na buli mulimu ogw’okukkiriza mu maanyi, <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PHP 2:9-11">Baf 2:9-11</ref></char></note>erinnya lya Mukama waffe Yesu liryoke ligulumizibwe mu mmwe, nammwe muweebwe ekitiibwa mu ye, ng’ekisa kya Katonda waffe ne Mukama waffe Yesu Kristo bwe kiri.</para>
  <chapter number="2" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Ebikolwa by’omulabe wa Kristo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MRK 13:27">Mak 13:27</ref>; <ref loc="1TH 4:15-17">1Bs 4:15-17</ref></char>
    </note>Kaakano abooluganda, ku by’okukomawo kwa Mukama waffe Yesu Kristo, era n’okukuŋŋaanyizibwa okumusisinkana, tubasaba <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:2 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TH 3:17">2Bs 3:17</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 1:8">1Ko 1:8</ref></char></note>muleme okweraliikirira wadde emitima okubeewanika newaakubadde olw’omwoyo, newaakubadde olw’ekigambo wadde olw’ebbaluwa, ebirabika ng’ebivudde gye tuli, nga biranga nti olunaku lwa Mukama lutuuse. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:3 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 5:6-8">Bef 5:6-8</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="DAN 7:25">Dan 7:25</ref>; <ref loc="DAN 8:25">8:25</ref>; <ref loc="DAN 11:36">11:36</ref>; <ref loc="REV 13:5">Kub 13:5</ref>, <ref loc="REV 13:6">6</ref></char></note>Omuntu yenna tabalimbalimbanga mu ngeri yonna; kubanga okuggyako ng’obujeemu busoose okujja, n’omuntu oli ow’obujeemu, omwana w’okuzikirira ng’amaze okulabisibwa, <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:4 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 8:5">1Ko 8:5</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 14:13">Is 14:13</ref>, <ref loc="ISA 14:14">14</ref>; <ref loc="EZK 28:2">Ez 28:2</ref></char></note>oyo alivvoola Katonda ne yeegulumiza okusinga ebintu byonna nga yeeyita katonda oba ekissibwamu ekitiibwa atuule mu yeekaalu ya Katonda omwo nga yeefuula okuba Katonda.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>Temujjukira ng’ebyo nabibategeeza bwe nnali nammwe? <verse number="6" style="v"/>Era ekikyamuziyizza mukimanyi kubanga tagenda kujja okutuusa ng’ekiseera kye kituuse. <verse number="7" style="v"/>Kubanga ekyama ky’obujeemu kyatandika dda okukola, naye ye yennyini tagenda kujja okutuusa oyo amuziyiza lw’aliva mu kkubo. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 11:4">Is 11:4</ref>; <ref loc="REV 19:15">Kub 19:15</ref></char></note>Olwo omuntu ow’obujeemu alyoke alabisibwe, Mukama waffe Yesu gw’alimalawo n’omukka ogw’omu kamwa ke n’amuzikiriza n’okulabisibwa kw’okujja kwe. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 24:24">Mat 24:24</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 4:48">Yk 4:48</ref></char></note>Omuntu oyo alijjira mu maanyi ga Setaani gonna n’akola obubonero n’eby’amagero, eby’obulimba, <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 1:18">1Ko 1:18</ref></char></note>era n’obulimba obwa buli ngeri obw’obutali butuukirivu eri abo abazikirizibwa, kubanga bagaana okukkiriza amazima okulokolebwa. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 1:28">Bar 1:28</ref></char></note>Katonda kyava abawaayo eri okubuzibwabuzibwa okw’amaanyi bakkirize eby’obulimba. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 1:32">Bar 1:32</ref></char></note>Era bonna balyoke basalirwe omusango olw’okukkiriza obulimba, ne bagaana amazima ne basanyukira okukola ebitali bya butuukirivu.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:13 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 1:4">Bef 1:4</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TH 5:9">1Bs 5:9</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">c </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1PE 1:2">1Pe 1:2</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Naye kitugwanidde okwebazanga Katonda ennaku zonna ku lwammwe, abooluganda abaagalwa mu Mukama waffe, kubanga Katonda yabalondera obulokozi okuva ku lubereberye, ng’abatukuza olw’okukola kw’Omwoyo n’okukkiriza amazima, <verse number="14" style="v"/>ge yabayitira ng’ayita mu Njiri yaffe mulyoke mufune ekitiibwa kya Mukama waffe Yesu Kristo. <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:15 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 16:13">1Ko 16:13</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 11:2">1Ko 11:2</ref></char></note>Noolwekyo abooluganda, munywererenga ku ebyo bye twabayigiriza mu bbaluwa zaffe oba mu bigambo byaffe.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 3:16">Yk 3:16</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Kale Mukama waffe Yesu Kristo yennyini, ne Katonda Kitaffe eyatwagala n’atuwa essanyu n’essuubi eddungi olw’ekisa kye, <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:17 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TH 3:2">1Bs 3:2</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TH 3:3">2Bs 3:3</ref></char></note>abazzeemu amaanyi, era abanywezenga mu buli kye mukola ne mu buli kigambo ekirungi.</para>
  <chapter number="3" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Okusabirwanga</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:1 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TH 4:1">1Bs 4:1</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TH 5:25">1Bs 5:25</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">c </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TH 1:8">1Bs 1:8</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Abooluganda, eky’enkomerero, mutusabirenga, ekigambo kya Mukama kibune mangu era Mukama agulumizibwenga, nga bw’agulumizibwa mu mmwe, <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 15:31">Bar 15:31</ref></char></note>tulyoke tununulibwe okuva mu bakozi b’ebibi, kubanga si bonna abakkiriza. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:3 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 1:9">1Ko 1:9</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 5:37">Mat 5:37</ref></char></note>Naye Mukama waffe mwesigwa, alibanyweza mmwe era anaabawonyanga Setaani. <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 2:3">2Ko 2:3</ref></char></note>Era twesiga nga Mukama waffe, abakozesa ebyo bye twabayigiriza era nga munaabikolanga bulijjo. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CH 29:18">1By 29:18</ref></char></note>Mukama waffe aluŋŋamyenga emitima gyammwe mu kutegeera okwagala kwa Katonda, n’obugumiikiriza obuva eri Kristo.</para>
  <para style="s1">Abalabula obutagayaalanga</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:6 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 5:4">1Ko 5:4</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 16:17">Bar 16:17</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">c </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">nny 7, 11 </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">d </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 11:2">1Ko 11:2</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Abooluganda abaagalwa, mbakuutira mu linnya lya Mukama waffe Yesu Kristo ne mu buyinza bwe, mwewalenga abagayaavu abatayagala kukola mirimu ne balemwa okugoberera ekyokulabirako kye twabateerawo. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 4:16">1Ko 4:16</ref></char></note>Kubanga mmwe bennyini mumanyi bulungi bwe kibagwanira okutugobereranga ng’ekyokulabirako kyammwe, kubanga temwatulaba nga twegomba okulya ebyo bye tutakoleredde, <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 18:3">Bik 18:3</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 4:28">Bef 4:28</ref></char></note>tetwakkiriza kulya mmere ya muntu yenna awatali kumusasula. Twafubanga nnyo ne tukoowa nga tukola emirimu emisana n’ekiro tulyoke tufunemu bye twetaaga okukozesa, era tuleme kuzitoowerera muntu n’omu ku mmwe. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:9 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 9:4-14">1Ko 9:4-14</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false">nny 7</char></note>Si kubanga tetwalina buyinza okubagamba mmwe okutuliisa, naye twayagala mutulabireko nga bwe kibagwanidde okukolanga. <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:10 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TH 3:4">1Bs 3:4</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TH 4:11">1Bs 4:11</ref></char></note>Era ne bwe twali gye muli eyo, twabakuutira nti omuntu yenna bw’agaananga okukola emirimu, n’okulya talyanga.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">nny 6, 7; <ref loc="1TI 5:13">1Ti 5:13</ref></char>
    </note>Kyokka tuwulira nti mu mmwe mulimu abagayaavu abatayagala kukola, aboonoona ebiseera byabwe mu kusaasaanya eŋŋambo. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:12 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TH 4:1">1Bs 4:1</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TH 4:11">1Bs 4:11</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 4:28">Bef 4:28</ref></char></note>Mu linnya lya Mukama waffe, tubeegayirira era tubakuutira abali bwe batyo, okukolanga emirimu n’obunyiikivu n’obuteefu balyoke balyenga ebyo bye bakoleredde. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GAL 6:9">Bag 6:9</ref></char></note>Naye mmwe temukoowanga kukola bulungi abooluganda abaagalwa.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">nny 6</char>
    </note>Era omuntu yenna bw’atagonderanga biragiro byaffe mu bbaluwa eno, oyo mumwetegereze, muleme kukolagananga naye, ensonyi ziryoke zimukwate. <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GAL 6:1">Bag 6:1</ref>; <ref loc="1TH 5:14">1Bs 5:14</ref></char></note>So temumuyisanga nga mulabe wammwe naye mumubuulirirenga ng’owooluganda eyetaaga okulabulwa.</para>
  <para style="s1">Eky’enkomerero</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:16 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 15:33">Bar 15:33</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="RUT 2:4">Lus 2:4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Kale Mukama nannyini mirembe abawenga emirembe mu byonna. Mukama abeerenga nammwe mwenna.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 16:21">1Ko 16:21</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Kuno kwe kulamusa kwange, nze Pawulo, mu mukono gwange, bwe ntyo bwe nkola ku nkomerero z’ebbaluwa zange zonna okulaga nti zivudde gye ndi. Bwe nti bwe mpandiika.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>Ekisa kya Mukama waffe Yesu Kristo kibeerenga nammwe mwenna.</para>
</usx>
